  "title": "Equipment Technician / Technologist (12-hrs shift / 3 years contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>First line troubleshooting for equipment-related issues</li><li>Execute scheduled and unscheduled equipment maintenance and Post PM process recovery</li><li>Responsible for equipment uptime and liaison with process control team and equipment vendors for resolving escalations and SPC deviations.</li><li>Works with process module development team, process control team and vendor to ensure flawless operations.</li><li>Support internal audits as needed for ISO certification.</li><li>Able to work under shift independently.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Electrical and Electronics, Mechanical, Mechatronics Engineering</li><li>Preferably with minimum 2 years of semiconductor equipment engineering experience (in the domain of Etch, PVD, PECVD) with hands-on equipment troubleshooting experience</li><li>Systematic and logical thinking.</li><li>Candidate must be comfortable to communicate with inter-department at any technical level</li><li>Must be a self-starter, independent and self-motivated.</li></ul><p>GMP Technologies (S) Pte Ltd | EA Licence 11C3793 | EA Personnel: Novita Widjaja | Registration No: R22105960</p><p><em>This is in partnership with the Employment and Employability Institute Pte Ltd (e2i).</em></p><p><em>e2i is the empowering network for workers and employers seeking employment and employability solutions. e2i serves as a bridge between workers and employers, connecting with workers to offer job security through job-matching, career guidance and skills upgrading services, and partnering employers to address their manpower needs through recruitment, training, and job redesign solutions. e2i is a tripartite initiative of the National Trades Union Congress set up to support nation-wide manpower and skills upgrading initiatives.</em></p><p><em>By applying for this role, you consent to GMP Recruitment Services (S) Pte Ltds </em><a href=\"https://www.gmprecruit.com/legal/privacy-policy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>PDPA</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"https://us-west-2.protection.sophos.com/?d=e2i.com.sg&u=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZTJpLmNvbS5zZy9wZHBhLw==&i=NThlNDdhOGMyYmI5N2YwZmQxZDk4NjQw&t=cWdqRFV0Uy80RjN3MDlSYmM1dS85VTRxVTRoYVlXdWFyWTYzaGlVS3k0TT0=&h=1ad0460f503340658fbeab159c31256f&s=AVNPUEhUT0NFTkNSWVBUSVaVGQEVMuPAipiPENS4aadnRg3RqoiWpHBKgNtumWhHjA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>e2is PDPA</em></a><em>.</em></p>",
